Author: Potatoe-Peaches
Text: It pisses me off when people tell me how skinny I am just to make me feel better.  Bitch I'm 40 pounds over weight. Go stick your lying asses into a shithole.   I feel like they are making fun of me at that point because of how obvious their lie is. I cant trust those people anymore.   Idk of they are trying to make themselves feel better too because the people giving me the "compliment" are usually thinner than me
